  <role>
    Spaarke platform DevOps engineer. Familiar with Azure resource provisioning, Key Vault secrets, App Service config, PowerShell deploy scripts.
  </role>

  <goal>
    `docs/guides/ai-search-azure-setup.md` exists as operator-ready guide covering all FR-02 sections.
  </goal>

  <context>
