      Currently no single doc owns AI Search provisioning. This guide is what an operator reads to set up AI Search in dev/staging/prod/demo.
      Phase 3 Deploy-AllIndexes.ps1 will reference this guide; Phase 1 establishes the doc skeleton.
    </background>
